%o A398080 (PARI) log(2)^5/15 - log(2)^3*zeta(2)/3 - 7*log(2)^2*zeta(3)/8 + 15*log(2)*zeta(4)/32 - 31*zeta(5)/64 - 7*zeta(2)*zeta(3)/16 + 2*log(2)*polylog(4, 1/2) + 2*polylog(5, 1/2)
